    <item>
      <title>中国总理下令采取更多措施遏制股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/china-s-premier-calls-for-better-measures-to-arrest-stock-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国内地基准沪深300指数周一触及五年低点后，中国总理李强要求当局采取更“有力”的措施来稳定中国低迷的股市和投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/china-s-premier-calls-for-better-measures-to-arrest-stock-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马哈蒂尔称儿子的马来西亚腐败调查是出于政治驱动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/malaysia-s-mahathir-says-son-s-graft-probe-is-politically-driven</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚前总理马哈蒂尔·穆罕默德表示，国家反腐败机构对他儿子商业活动的调查是出于政治动机，他不知道有任何其他原因需要采取这样的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/malaysia-s-mahathir-says-son-s-graft-probe-is-politically-driven</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 09:45:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国冬季山体滑坡两名幸存者获救，11人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-22/urgent-landslide-in-mountainous-southwestern-china-buries-44-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京（美联社）——周一，中国西南部偏远山区发生山体滑坡，冰冻天气中导致 47 人被埋，造成至少 11 人死亡，两名幸存者获救。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-22/urgent-landslide-in-mountainous-southwestern-china-buries-44-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 03:22:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
